{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_018kBXd7KG7GCcquJZDknLi6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a thorough understanding of the codebase. Let me update the todos and begin the migration. This is a complex Jakarta EE application with:\n\n- **CDI** (`@Inject`, `@ApplicationScoped`, `@Produces`) -> Spring DI (`@Autowired`, `@Component`, `@Bean`)\n- **EJB** (`@Stateless`, `@Singleton`, `@MessageDriven`) -> Spring `@Service`, `@Component`\n- **JPA** with `@PersistenceContext` -> Spring Data JPA or Spring-managed EntityManager\n- **JMS** queues -> Spring Events (simpler async event system)\n- **JAX-RS** (`@Path`, `@GET`) -> Spring MVC (`@RestController`, `@GetMapping`)\n- **JSF/PrimeFaces** -> Replace with Thymeleaf or just REST endpoints (JSF is incompatible with Spring Boot)\n- **Jakarta Batch** -> Spring Batch or scheduled tasks\n- **SSE via JAX-RS** -> Spring MVC SseEmitter"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3117,"cache_read_input_tokens":73563,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":3117,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":752},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cb64f649-59c6-4f3a-a73b-f24ff02d923c","uuid":"06e8ab31-9b62-41e5-9b8b-029a6c97c96b"}
