{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0158w2AnaFxHtraZ1gRJFZrU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01HeGNYFCQf8k21AeGfWgF9Z","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Migrate domain model files","prompt":"I am migrating a Jakarta EE application to Spring Boot 2.7.x. I need you to write the following migrated Java source files. The base directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nIMPORTANT: Spring Boot 2.7.x still uses javax.persistence, javax.validation etc - NOT jakarta.* namespaces. So JPA annotations stay as javax.persistence.*.\n\nThe key changes needed for domain model files:\n- Remove any EJB-specific annotations  \n- CDI @Inject stays as-is or switches to Spring @Autowired\n- @ApplicationScoped -> @Component or @Service\n- Keep all JPA annotations (javax.persistence.*) as they are\n- @ApplicationException (EJB) needs to be removed (not available in Spring)\n\nPlease READ the following files first, then WRITE the migrated versions:\n\n1. **Cargo.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/Cargo.java\n   - This is a JPA entity, should need minimal changes. Just ensure imports are correct.\n\n2. **TrackingId.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/TrackingId.java\n   - Embeddable value object, minimal changes.\n\n3. **Itinerary.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/Itinerary.java  \n   - Embeddable, minimal changes.\n\n4. **Leg.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/Leg.java\n   - JPA entity, minimal changes.\n\n5. **RouteSpecification.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/RouteSpecification.java\n   - Embeddable, minimal changes.\n\n6. **Delivery.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/Delivery.java\n   - Embeddable, minimal changes.\n\n7. **HandlingActivity.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/HandlingActivity.java\n   - Embeddable, minimal changes.\n\n8. **TransportStatus.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/TransportStatus.java\n   - Enum, no changes needed.\n\n9. **RoutingStatus.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/RoutingStatus.java\n   - Enum, no changes needed.\n\n10. **CargoRepository.java** - Read from src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/cargo/CargoRepository.java\n    - Interface, no changes needed.\n\nFor each file, read it first, make necessary changes, and write it back. If no changes are needed, leave the file as-is. Report what you changed.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":410,"cache_read_input_tokens":81117,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":410,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2325},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cb64f649-59c6-4f3a-a73b-f24ff02d923c","uuid":"e9dedb5c-64a9-4e3c-be51-f4100c1ccfae"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0158w2AnaFxHtraZ1gRJFZrU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01DAbb751bLM9vT33d25x5vB","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Migrate handling/voyage/location domain","prompt":"I am migrating a Jakarta EE application to Spring Boot 2.7.x. I need you to write the following migrated Java source files. The base directory is /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output\n\nIMPORTANT: Spring Boot 2.7.x still uses javax.persistence, javax.validation etc - NOT jakarta.* namespaces. So JPA annotations stay as javax.persistence.*.\n\nKey changes needed:\n- Remove @ApplicationException annotations (EJB-specific, not in Spring)\n- CDI @Inject -> can stay as @Inject (Spring supports it) or use @Autowired\n- @ApplicationScoped -> @Component or @Service\n- Keep all JPA annotations (javax.persistence.*) as they are\n\nPlease READ the following files first, then WRITE the migrated versions:\n\n**Handling domain:**\n1. HandlingEvent.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/HandlingEvent.java - JPA entity, minimal changes\n2. HandlingHistory.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/HandlingHistory.java - Value object, minimal changes\n3. HandlingEventRepository.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/HandlingEventRepository.java - Interface, no changes\n4. HandlingEventFactory.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/HandlingEventFactory.java - Change @ApplicationScoped to @Component, @Inject to @Autowired\n5. CannotCreateHandlingEventException.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/CannotCreateHandlingEventException.java - REMOVE @ApplicationException annotation import and usage\n6. UnknownVoyageException.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/UnknownVoyageException.java - Same, remove @ApplicationException\n7. UnknownCargoException.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/UnknownCargoException.java - Same\n8. UnknownLocationException.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/handling/UnknownLocationException.java - Same\n\n**Voyage domain:**\n9. Voyage.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/Voyage.java - JPA entity, minimal\n10. VoyageNumber.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/VoyageNumber.java - Embeddable, minimal\n11. VoyageRepository.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/VoyageRepository.java - Interface, no changes\n12. Schedule.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/Schedule.java - Embeddable, minimal\n13. CarrierMovement.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/CarrierMovement.java - JPA entity, minimal\n14. SampleVoyages.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/voyage/SampleVoyages.java - Utility, no changes\n\n**Location domain:**\n15. Location.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/location/Location.java - JPA entity, minimal\n16. UnLocode.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/location/UnLocode.java - Embeddable, minimal\n17. SampleLocations.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/location/SampleLocations.java - Utility, no changes\n18. LocationRepository.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/model/location/LocationRepository.java - Interface, no changes\n\n**Domain service and shared:**\n19. RoutingService.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/service/RoutingService.java - Interface, no changes\n20. Specification.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/Specification.java - No changes\n21. AbstractSpecification.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/AbstractSpecification.java - No changes\n22. AndSpecification.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/AndSpecification.java - No changes\n23. OrSpecification.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/OrSpecification.java - No changes\n24. NotSpecification.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/NotSpecification.java - No changes\n25. DomainObjectUtils.java - src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/DomainObjectUtils.java - No changes\n\nFor each file, read it first, make only necessary changes (primarily removing @ApplicationException and changing CDI annotations to Spring annotations where needed), and write it back. Report what you changed.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":410,"cache_read_input_tokens":81117,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":410,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2325},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cb64f649-59c6-4f3a-a73b-f24ff02d923c","uuid":"57df867e-df37-41ef-bfd0-d165e1316faa"}
