{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01T7imA6r6jCASusUKByT48m","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/domain/shared/AbstractSpecification.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.shared;\n     2→\n     3→/**\n     4→ * Abstract base implementation of composite {@link Specification} with default implementations for\n     5→ * {@code and}, {@code or} and {@code not}.\n     6→ */\n     7→public abstract class AbstractSpecification<T> implements Specification<T> {\n     8→\n     9→  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n    10→  @Override\n    11→  public abstract boolean isSatisfiedBy(T t);\n    12→\n    13→  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n    14→  @Override\n    15→  public Specification<T> and(Specification<T> specification) {\n    16→    return new AndSpecification<>(this, specification);\n    17→  }\n    18→\n    19→  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n    20→  @Override\n    21→  public Specification<T> or(Specification<T> specification) {\n    22→    return new OrSpecification<>(this, specification);\n    23→  }\n    24→\n    25→  /** {@inheritDoc} */\n    26→  @Override\n    27→  public Specification<T> not(Specification<T> specification) {\n    28→    return new NotSpecification<>(specification);\n    29→  }\n    30→}\n    31→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01DAbb751bLM9vT33d25x5vB","session_id":"cb64f649-59c6-4f3a-a73b-f24ff02d923c","uuid":"a296fca1-4d44-4c88-9be4-9448cfc30d4b"}
