{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01HiyZbdFjggUVLWJpzxKKyF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_018qbFmSaQRdhmbWgN6qCDyC","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n\nimport java.util.logging.Level;\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\nimport org.springframework.context.event.EventListener;\nimport org.springframework.scheduling.annotation.Async;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\n@Component\npublic class MisdirectedCargoConsumer {\n\n  private static final Logger logger =\n      Logger.getLogger(MisdirectedCargoConsumer.class.getName());\n\n  @Async\n  @EventListener\n  public void onCargoMisdirected(JmsApplicationEvents.CargoMisdirectedEvent event) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo with tracking ID {0} misdirected.\", event.getTrackingId());\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":697,"cache_read_input_tokens":41602,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":697,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":338},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014FNHC1EwVT2yLV4ie2q9aJ","session_id":"cb64f649-59c6-4f3a-a73b-f24ff02d923c","uuid":"a4a4f3b6-8b12-4495-94db-7d4a9383b7c5"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_018qbFmSaQRdhmbWgN6qCDyC","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n     2→\n     3→import java.util.logging.Level;\n     4→import java.util.logging.Logger;\n     5→import org.springframework.context.event.EventListener;\n     6→import org.springframework.scheduling.annotation.Async;\n     7→import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n     8→\n     9→@Component\n    10→public class MisdirectedCargoConsumer {\n    11→\n    12→  private static final Logger logger =\n    13→      Logger.getLogger(MisdirectedCargoConsumer.class.getName());\n    14→\n    15→  @Async\n    16→  @EventListener\n    17→  public void onCargoMisdirected(JmsApplicationEvents.CargoMisdirectedEvent event) {\n    18→    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo with tracking ID {0} misdirected.\", event.getTrackingId());\n    19→  }\n    20→}\n    21→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014FNHC1EwVT2yLV4ie2q9aJ","session_id":"cb64f649-59c6-4f3a-a73b-f24ff02d923c","uuid":"557c329e-7797-4d1f-ad77-ccf11828d05f"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Sza7KWb2edyqtgJwhieoCR","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All migration tasks are complete. Let me create a summary of the work:\n\n## Application Layer Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all files in the application layer from Jakarta EE to Spring Boot 2.7.x. Here's a detailed breakdown:\n\n### Files That Required No Changes (Verified)\n\n#### Interfaces\n1. **BookingService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/BookingService.java`)\n   - Interface with only javax.validation annotations\n   - No EJB or CDI annotations\n   - Compatible with Spring Boot 2.7.x as-is\n\n2. **CargoInspectionService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/CargoInspectionService.java`)\n   - Interface with only javax.validation annotations\n   - No changes needed\n\n3. **HandlingEventService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/HandlingEventService.java`)\n   - Interface with only javax.validation annotations\n   - No changes needed\n\n4. **ApplicationEvents.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/ApplicationEvents.java`)\n   - Pure interface, no annotations\n   - No changes needed\n\n#### Utility Classes\n5. **ApplicationSettings.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/ApplicationSettings.java`)\n   - JPA Entity with javax.persistence annotations\n   - Compatible with Spring Boot 2.7.x as-is\n\n6. **DateConverter.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/DateConverter.java`)\n   - Utility class with static methods\n   - No changes needed\n\n### Files Migrated\n\n#### Service Implementation Classes\n\n7. **DefaultBookingService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultBookingService.java`)\n   - **Changes made:**\n     - Removed `@Stateless` (EJB)\n     - Added `@Service` and `@Transactional` (Spring)\n     - Changed `@Inject` to `@Autowired`\n     - Removed `javax.ejb.Stateless` import\n     - Removed `javax.inject.Inject` import\n     - Added Spring imports: `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`, `org.springframework.stereotype.Service`, `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n   - **Business logic:** Unchanged\n\n8. **DefaultCargoInspectionService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultCargoInspectionService.java`)\n   - **Changes made:**\n     - Removed `@Stateless` (EJB)\n     - Added `@Service` and `@Transactional` (Spring)\n     - Changed `@Inject` to `@Autowired`\n     - Removed `javax.ejb.Stateless` import\n     - Removed `javax.inject.Inject` import\n     - Added Spring imports\n   - **Business logic:** Unchanged\n\n9. **DefaultHandlingEventService.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultHandlingEventService.java`)\n   - **Changes made:**\n     - Removed `@Stateless` (EJB)\n     - Added `@Service` and `@Transactional` (Spring)\n     - Changed `@Inject` to `@Autowired`\n     - Removed `javax.ejb.Stateless` import\n     - Removed `javax.inject.Inject` import\n     - Added Spring imports\n   - **Business logic:** Unchanged\n\n#### Configuration Classes\n\n10. **RestConfiguration.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/RestConfiguration.java`)\n    - **Changes made:**\n      - Completely rewritten for Spring Boot\n      - Removed JAX-RS `@ApplicationPath` and Jersey-specific configuration\n      - Now a minimal `@Configuration` class with documentation explaining that Spring Boot handles REST auto-configuration\n      - Kept empty for structural compatibility\n\n#### Startup/Initialization Classes\n\n11. **SampleDataGenerator.java** (`/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/SampleDataGenerator.java`)\n    - **Changes made:**\n      - Removed `@Singleton` and `@Startup` (EJB)\n      - Added `@Component` (Spring)\n      - Implemented `CommandLineRunner` interface\n      - Renamed `@PostConstruct` method logic to `run(String... args)` method\n      - Changed `@Inject` to `@Autowired`\n      - Kept `@PersistenceContext` for EntityManager (Spring supports this)\n      - Added `@Transactional` on the `run()` method\n      - Removed EJB imports: `javax.annotation.PostConstruct`, `javax.ejb.Singleton`, `javax.ejb.Startup`, `javax.ejb.TransactionAttribute`, `javax.ejb.TransactionAttributeType`, `javax.inject.Inject`\n      - Added Spring imports: `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`, `org.springframework.boot.CommandLineRunner`, `org.springframework.stereotype.Component`, `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n    - **Business logic:** Unchanged - all sample data loading logic remains identical\n\n### Key Migration Patterns Applied\n\n1. **EJB to Spring Service**: `@Stateless` → `@Service` + `@Transactional`\n2. **Dependency Injection**: `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n3. **Startup Logic**: `@Singleton` + `@Startup` + `@PostConstruct` → `@Component` + `CommandLineRunner.run()`\n4. **Persistence**: Kept `@PersistenceContext` as Spring supports it\n5. **Validation**: All `javax.validation.*` and `javax.persistence.*` annotations remain unchanged (correct for Spring Boot 2.7.x)\n\nAll business logic has been preserved exactly as it was in the original implementation. The migration focused solely on replacing Jakarta EE/EJB annotations and patterns with their Spring Boot equivalents."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cb64f649-59c6-4f3a-a73b-f24ff02d923c","uuid":"987c43ae-8722-49a6-9ac4-82b05a47b9fd"}
